# Copy to ".dev.vars" for LOCAL testing with `npx wrangler dev`.
# (.dev.vars is gitignored. In production these are set with `wrangler secret put`.)
#
# Leave RESEND_API_KEY blank locally to run in "dry-run" mode: emails are logged
# to the console instead of actually sent, so you can test the flow safely.

RESEND_API_KEY=
SIGNING_SECRET=local-dev-secret-change-me
OWNER_EMAIL=your-test-inbox@example.com
